:INFO
Make Your Koji Rice
Steam 200 g of polished short-grain rice until just cooked but not mushy. Cool to 30 C \
(86 F) and inoculate with 2 g of dried koji-kin spores. Spread the inoculated rice \
thinly on a clean tray, cover loosely with a damp cloth, and keep at 28 to 32 C (82

