:INFO
Build the Starter Mash (Shubo)
Combine 75 g of steamed rice, 100 g of your finished koji rice, 165 ml of cold water, \
and a small packet of sake yeast or dry wine yeast. Mix in a sanitized jar and keep at \
10 to 15 C (50 to 59 F) for 10 to 14 days, stirring daily. Cold temperatures

