:INFO
Build the Main Mash in Three Additions
Over three days, add steamed rice, koji rice, and water to the starter in increasing \
amounts. Day one: add 200 g rice, 100 g koji, and 240 ml water. Day two: rest with no \
additions. Day three: add 350 g rice, 170 g koji, and 450 ml water. This three-step

